    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain provides an engaging, analog experience. The Double VANOS system has been recently serviced for precise cam timing, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, offering the communicative feedback characteristic of the M-chassis. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust and ready for the circuit or the canyon.",
